- I think it could be done.

966
01:10:29,640 --> 01:10:33,792
Let's say we found the guy and he is great,
but look, the songs?

967
01:10:33,920 --> 01:10:36,718
Couldn't use the old recordings
I made years ago, right?

968
01:10:36,840 --> 01:10:38,432
I'm afraid it is.

969
