- Anything else, pal?

980
01:11:12,760 --> 01:11:15,797
Those Mammies, those Rock-A-Byes,
you've got to give out.

981
01:11:15,920 --> 01:11:18,559
- You think you couldn't do that?
- Think I couldn't do it?

982
01:11:18,680 --> 01:11:20,875
